        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The documentation mentions that Zend_Application_Resource_Modules will create a Zend_Application_Module_Autoloader instance, and likewise, it is what I would expect it to do, but it isn't. The only thing that I can see it doing is instansiating the module bootstrap if it exists. Are we supposed to create the Zend_Application_Module_Autoloader instance in the module bootstrap? If so, the documentation such be modified to state this.\n\nThanks."
